column2: SELECT Galaxy.objID, Galaxy.ra, Galaxy.dec, Galaxy.dered_u, Galaxy.dered_g, Galaxy.dered_r, Galaxy.dered_i, Galaxy.dered_z, Galaxy.modelMagErr_u, Galaxy.modelMagErr_g, Galaxy.modelMagErr_r, Galaxy.modelMagErr_i, Galaxy.modelMagErr_z, Galaxy.cModelMag_i-Galaxy.extinction_i as i_cmod,    Galaxy.psfMag_i-Galaxy.extinction_i as i_psf, Galaxy.fiber2Mag_i-Galaxy.extinction_i as i_fiber2, Galaxy.expMag_i-Galaxy.extinction_i as i_exp, Galaxy.petroRad_i, Galaxy.deVRad_i,    Galaxy.expRad_i, Galaxy.deVAB_i, Galaxy.expAB_i, Galaxy.lnLStar_i, Galaxy.lnLExp_i, Galaxy.lnLDev_i, Galaxy.sky_i, Galaxy.psffwhm_r, Galaxy.extinction_i,    wiseForcedTarget.w1_mag, wiseForcedTarget.w1_mag_err, wiseForcedTarget.w2_mag, wiseForcedTarget.w2_mag_err   into Large_galaxy_sample_with_errors_nocuts_two FROM Galaxy JOIN wiseForcedTarget on Galaxy.objID= wiseForcedTarget.objID  WHERE Galaxy.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND (Galaxy.mode != # OR Galaxy.type != # OR Galaxy.insideMask != #) OFFSET # ROWS
